Here autumn whispered to me and the wind and said “I fall; but always rise again.”

Happy Thanksgiving! (If you dont celebrate,cheers to another day alive on this beautiful planet!) I spent the last 4 months living/traveling in my van seeing much of the beauty this country has to offer and was the second year in a row I was able to do this. I have safely made it to Florida for the holidays, so I want to take a moment to say I am thankful for all of my friends, family, all of you, and everyone who has supported me on my journey (even the haters) Without you I could not have done it. Thank you! The point of my posts and showing how I’m living is not to show off that I am living some glamorous life (it is definitely not all glamorous) but to inspire. 5 years ago I was a homeless jailbird, addicted to drugs and had nothing except the clothes on my back. This is no exaggeration just truth. 3 years ago I was stuck in a bullshit job making 10 dollars an hour getting told that ”I couldn't do anything,I was a loser, no one liked me, that I was no good and would never be nothing.” I was going through the motions doing nothing productive with my life. And now today in such a short period of time I have grown and created a life where I do what I want whenever I want and I answer to no one except the weather as well as the moon and sun cause they control the tides. I achieved this through self belief, hard work, persistence, doing my best to stay positive, helping others, putting out the energy and vibe that I wanted coming back to me, and most of all dreaming big day and night and chasing those dreams with conviction. Today be thankful and grateful for everyone/everything that you have in your life. If you are not living your best life take a deep breath and think to yourself what are your dreams? What do you really want in life? What do you truly desire? Wake up and take action. There is no big secret, I have no special power or specific edge over anyone, I'm uneducated and untrained, coming from nothing to having everything I could ever ask for. I promise you without a doubt if I was able to do this ANYONE can. I give you my word and I will stand by it, dreams do come true. So LETS GO! #LIVEFREE and #STAYWILD
It’s better to have a short life that is full of what you like doing, than a long life spent in a miserable way.
